Bunu JavaPlugin sınıfınızda `onCommand` metodunu ezerek veya bir `CommandExecutor` oluşturarak yapabilirsiniz.

```java
@Override
public boolean onCommand(CommandSender sender, Command command, String label, String[] args) {
    if (command.getName().equalsIgnoreCase("info")) {
        if (sender instanceof Player player) {
            ItemStack item = new ItemStack(Material.IRON_INGOT, 10);
            player.getInventory().addItem(item);
            player.sendMessage("Eşyaları aldın!");
            return true;
        }
    }
    return false;
}
```

You can achieve this by overriding `onCommand` in your JavaPlugin class or creating a `CommandExecutor`.

